headline: 3 Companies Including Zscaler That May Be Priced Below Estimated Value
summary: In July 2025, the U.S. stock market exhibited a mix of resilience and volatility, with major indices like the S&P 500 and Nasdaq hitting record highs despite late-month slumps driven by fluctuating tech earnings and economic data. Amidst this backdrop of strong corporate performance yet cautious investor sentiment due to tariff uncertainties, identifying stocks that may be undervalued could present opportunities for investors seeking value in a complex market landscape.
